  #     `registry.gitlab.com`
  #
  #   * Kubernetes (`k8s`) – `registry.k8s.io`
  #
  #   * Microsoft Azure Container Registry (`azure-container-registry`) –
  #     `<custom>.azurecr.io`
  #
  #   * Quay (`quay`) – `quay.io`
