  #     client.wait_until(waiter_name, params, {
  #       max_attempts: 5,
  #       delay: 5,
  #     })
  #
  # ## Callbacks
  #
  # You can be notified before each polling attempt and before each
  # delay. If you throw `:success` or `:failure` from these callbacks,
  # it will terminate the waiter.
